  <brief_title>Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy in Non Small Cell Lung Cancer (NSCLC) Stages IB, IIA, IIB, and IIIA/T3</brief_title>
  <official_title>Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy in Resectable NSCLC Stages IB, IIA, IIB, and IIIA/T3 But Not IIIA/N2</official_title>
  <sponsors>
