  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomised trial of chemotherapy or not before surgery in early resectable stages of NSCLC
      (IB, IIA, IIB, and IIIA/N2).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Randomisation between 3 courses of neoadjuvant Carboplatin plus Paclitaxel or no chemotherapy
      before surgery.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
