  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  NSCLC

          -  Stages IB, IIA, IIB, IIIA/T3

          -  Lung function test allowing surgery

          -  Age 18-75 years

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Poor lung function

          -  Performance status 3-4

          -  Mediastinal lymph node involvement
      </textblock>
